---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ueber uns" description="Erfahren Sie mehr ueber noadges - Ihre Digitalagentur fuer Webentwicklung, Design und digitale Strategie.">

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Ueber uns</span>
      <h1>Wir sind <span class="gradient-text">noadges</span></h1>
      <p>Eine Digitalagentur mit Leidenschaft fuer Innovation, Design und Technologie. Seit ueber 5 Jahren gestalten wir die digitale Zukunft unserer Kunden.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-content">
          <span class="section-label">Unsere Geschichte</span>
          <h2>Von der Vision zur Realitaet</h2>
          <p>Gegruendet mit der Ueberzeugung, dass digitale Produkte nicht nur funktionieren, sondern begeistern muessen. Wir kombinieren technische Exzellenz mit kreativem Design, um Loesungen zu schaffen, die einen echten Unterschied machen.</p>
          <p>Unser Team aus Entwicklern, Designern und Strategen arbeitet eng mit unseren Kunden zusammen, um ihre Vision in massgeschneiderte digitale Erlebnisse zu verwandeln.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
          <div class="about-image-placeholder">
            <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Unsere Werte</span>
        <h2>Wofuer wir stehen</h2>
        <p>Diese Prinzipien leiten uns in jedem Projekt.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card value-card animate-in">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Qualitaet</h3>
          <p>Wir liefern nur Arbeit ab, auf die wir stolz sind. Jedes Detail zaehlt.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card value-card animate-in">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 006 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9M13.73 21a2 2 0 01-3.46 0"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Innovation</h3>
          <p>Wir nutzen die neuesten Technologien und Trends, um zukunftssichere Loesungen zu schaffen.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card value-card animate-in">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Leidenschaft</h3>
          <p>Wir lieben, was wir tun. Diese Begeisterung spiegelt sich in jedem Projekt wider.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card value-card animate-in">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Transparenz</h3>
          <p>Offene Kommunikation und ehrliches Feedback sind die Basis unserer Zusammenarbeit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card value-card animate-in">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 014 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 014-10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Nachhaltigkeit</h3>
          <p>Wir entwickeln Loesungen, die langfristig funktionieren und skalierbar sind.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card value-card animate-in">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Teamwork</h3>
          <p>Gemeinsam erreichen wir mehr. Wir arbeiten als Team - intern und mit unseren Kunden.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Das Team</span>
        <h2>Die Menschen hinter noadges</h2>
        <p>Unser Team aus Experten mit Leidenschaft fuer digitale Exzellenz.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-4 team-grid">
        <div class="team-card animate-in">
          <div class="team-avatar">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-muted)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Max Mustermann</h3>
          <span class="team-role">Geschaeftsfuehrer & Stratege</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card animate-in">
          <div class="team-avatar">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-muted)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Lisa Schmidt</h3>
          <span class="team-role">Lead Designerin</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card animate-in">
          <div class="team-avatar">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-muted)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Tom Weber</h3>
          <span class="team-role">Senior Entwickler</span>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card animate-in">
          <div class="team-avatar">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-muted)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Sarah Klein</h3>
          <span class="team-role">Projektmanagerin</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Numbers -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-4 numbers-grid">
        <div class="number-item animate-in">
          <strong>50+</strong>
          <span>Projekte abgeschlossen</span>
        </div>
        <div class="number-item animate-in">
          <strong>30+</strong>
          <span>Zufriedene Kunden</span>
        </div>
        <div class="number-item animate-in">
          <strong>5+</strong>
          <span>Jahre Erfahrung</span>
        </div>
        <div class="number-item animate-in">
          <strong>4</strong>
          <span>Teamexperten</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-image {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-image-placeholder {
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .value-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--accent-glow);
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .team-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  .team-avatar {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }

  .team-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .team-role {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .number-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .number-item strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: var(--gradient-accent);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .number-item span {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
